# instalar o NVM

--- Curl command:
curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.34.0/install.sh | bash

--- Wget command:
wget -qO- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/creationix/nvm/v0.34.0/install.sh | bash

--- Verifique o NVM na linha de comando

command -v nvm

--- Se estiver instalado, você receberá uma mensagem como:
nvm

--- Usando NVM

nvm ls-remote


--- Instalando alguma versão

nvm install <version>

--- Usar versão
nvm use alias default <version>
